author={T. K. J. Ting and G. B. Wang and M. H. Wang and C. P. Wu and C. K. Wang and C. W. Lo and L. C. Tien and D. M. Yuan and Y. C. Hsieh and J. S. Lai and W. P. Hsu and C. C. Huang and C. K. Chen and Y. F. Chou and D. M. Kwai and Z. Wang and W. Wu and S. Tomishima and P. Stolt and S. L. Lu}, 
